{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "x402-gateway-collection",
		"name": "x402 Payment Gateway",
		"description": "Complete test collection for the x402 BSV payment gateway reference implementation.\n\nThe default base URL is `http://localhost:8402`.\n\n## x402 Payment Flow\n1. GET /v1/expensive → 402 + X402-Challenge header\n2. POST /demo/build-proof with challenge → proof_header\n3. GET /v1/expensive with X402-Proof header → 200\n4. Replay same proof → 409 (double_spend)\n\n## Running the Collection\nUse the **Full Demo Flow** folder — run requests in sequence using Postman Collection Runner.\n\n## Modes\n- **Demo mode** (BROADCASTER=mock): pools auto-seeded, /demo/build-proof available\n- **Live mode** (BROADCASTER=woc): real BSV transactions, client must build proofs\n\n## RACE-01 Fix\nConcurrent nonce reservations return 202 (nonce_pending) instead of allowing race conditions.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8402",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "challengeEncoded",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "proofHeader",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
